00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:42.559
to actually write Python code, what kind of IDE to use. So this talk is a talk of good news,

00:02:42.559 --> 00:02:48.960
because in the intervening 10 years, the tooling in both of these areas has changed a lot, and

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:54.880
there are much better solutions. So let's dig into that first one first. This is a topic upon which

